  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dc2\u0dab \u0d87\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dba\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db4\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Do not send children to school if they have covid symptoms",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Pediatrician Dr. Deepal Perera says that children with symptoms of 'Covid' should not be sent to schools.",
        "The doctor said that if this is not done, there is a risk of the children getting sick."
      ],
